02:27.680 --> 02:39.700
Anna Maria Luisa è responsabile per la vasta collezione di arti medici che sono ora, oggi, nel palazzo e nella galleria di Florence.

02:39.700 --> 02:45.140
Without this woman Florence wouldn't be Florence.

02:45.940 --> 02:57.140
And so I'm very glad because also in the present, not also in the past, we search to improve this attention.

02:57.840 --> 03:06.140
Our administration, for example, is the first one who has made it by the 50% of women for the first time in the history of Florence.

03:07.440 --> 03:11.100
Unfortunately the mayor is a man, but nobody is perfect.

03:11.800 --> 03:15.320
I will remain a man, the mayor will change in the future.

03:16.740 --> 03:29.920
And I am very honored also because this place is a particular place not only for the history, but for the future.

03:29.920 --> 03:46.400
If I think about the fourth world conference, a woman in Beijing, I was very impressed by a speech of a woman who will always be in our hearts, Benazir Bhutto.

03:46.920 --> 03:55.820
Benazir Bhutto defined empowerment as the right to be independent, to be educated, to have choices in life.

03:57.560 --> 04:10.440
Empowerment is the right to have the opportunity to select a productive career, to own property, to participate in business, to flourish in the marketplace.

04:10.800 --> 04:13.480
Flourish is a very important word in Florence.

04:13.820 --> 04:18.480
We must shape a world free from exploitation and maltreatment of women.

04:18.480 --> 04:27.000
A world in which women have opportunities to rise to the highest level in politics, business, diplomacy and other spheres of life.

04:27.680 --> 04:34.520
Also in the speech of Hillary Clinton, we can search the expression flourish.

04:35.360 --> 04:40.720
If women are healthy and educated, their families will flourish.

04:41.560 --> 04:45.740
If women are free from violence, their families will flourish.

04:45.740 --> 04:56.100
If women have a chance to work and earn as full and equal partners in society, their families will flourish.

04:56.280 --> 05:00.500
When families flourish, communities and the nations will flourish.

05:01.160 --> 05:06.900
So I was very impressed because my city is Florence, the city of the flower.

05:08.040 --> 05:13.620
I hope in the city of the flower your wishes, your hopes.

05:13.620 --> 05:18.760
Let me say our wishes, our hopes may flourish.

05:19.280 --> 05:21.060
Thank you for coming. Enjoy your stay.

